			  entrance
title "The Dark Windy Entrance"
descr
"     Wild winds gust through this corner of a darkened corridor.  Blasts
of heat assail you from above while a bone chilling gust blows from the
east.  The hall is unlit but a faint glow from the east lights your way."

ALWAYS_LIGHT
flags {UNIT_FL_NO_WEATHER}
movement SECT_CITY
east to corridor descr "A faint glow lights your way east.";
end

			  corridor
title "The Dark Windy Corridor"
descr
"     Gale force winds strike your back with a biting cold.  You feel as if
you are being forced into the room ahead.  To the east the corridor appears to open into a huge chamber.  As the wind drives you forward you realize
a massive precipice looms ahead.  The air currents are too strong to return
west."

extra {"precipice", "chamber", "huge chamber"}
"The huge chamber ahead is indistinct in the dim light and the distance to the
far side of the chamber is indeterminable.  A chasm seems to stretch from the
end of the corridor to the edge of sight.  The cold air is pushing you rapidly
towards the edge."

flags {UNIT_FL_NO_WEATHER}
movement SECT_CITY
ALWAYS_LIGHT
east to edge1 descr "The bone chilling wind forces you towards the edge of a chasm.";
west to corridor descr "The wind pushes you back east.  There will be no returning this way.";
end

