			bridge
title "The Bridge of Faith"
descr
"     Suspended over the Abyss, the invisible Bridge of Faith supports your
weight by some ancient lost miracle of magic.  The Abyss seems to spiral
away below you and you tear your eyes away before the sight causes you to
lose your balance.  As your senses settle you realize that the vorpal winds
and piercing wails are no longer present.  The magic of the bridge seems to
be providing a magic shielding that uplifts your soul.  You believe this may
be a good place to rest.  By touch you find the bridge runs east and west."

extra {"bridge of faith", "faith bridge", "bridge"}
"Completely invisible to mortal eyes, the bridge is still reassuringly
present by touch.  It appears to run east and west."

