			platform
title "The Platform over the Center of the Abyss"
descr
"     From this viewpoint the sight of the Abyss is overwhelming.  Straight
down stretches into an infinity of darkness and hell.  Piercing screams and
shreaking wails draw your eyes to the edges of the hellish pit where the
faint glimmer of forsaken souls dot the icy black stone.  Occasionally a
glimmer dies as a soul is consumed by the netherworld creatures that feed
within the Abyss.  You force your gaze back to the platform to retain what
precious little is left of your sanity.  There does not appear to be any
exits from this platform."

extra {"platform"}
"This icy black slab of stone seems to defy gravity as it hovers here,
directly over the mouth of the Abyss."

extra {"abyss", "infinite", "darkness", "hell"}
"Dark, empty, and endless, the pit of all hell stretches before you causing
your senses to reel.  You quickly focus again upon your surroundings to avoid
losing your balance."

extra {"souls", "glimmer"}
"The light of the hapless tormented souls clinging to the edges of the Abyss
are visible below you.  Occasionally their screams are silenced as they are
devoured by the hideous scavengers of this hellish pit."

extra {"icy black stone", "black stone", "stone", "edges"}
"The edges of the Abyss are an icy black stone that seems to grow more sheer
as it descends further towards the depths of hell.  It seems as if it may be
possible to climb a reasonable distance into the Abyss, perhaps to help the
unfortunate souls trapped there."

extra {"netherworld creatures", "creatures", "scavengers"}
"Unimaginably hideous creatures roam the Abyss devouring the souls that have
not yet fallen.  They seem impervious to the vorpal winds that scour the edges
of the pit."
