			side1
title "Clinging to the Edge of the Abyss"
descr
"     Vorpal winds whip past and the wailing reaches a new cacophony.  The
infinite darkness below you sucks at your sanity as the chill saps your
strength.  Around you, hapless souls cling to the bare stone and lament
their fate.  Only your continuing concentration on remaining attached to
the edge of the Abyss keeps madness at bay.  An arms length above you is
the rim of the Abyss while down leads deeper into infinity.  A lateral
move may also be possible."

